        "Extended photo gallery on profiles",
        "Family booklet (1 to 2 times a year)",
        "You help keep the project alive"
      ],
      "faq": [
        {
          "q": "Do I have to pay to see the tree?",
          "a": "No. Viewing the tree, searching, consulting profiles (per the family's privacy settings) and contributing are free for all members, for life. We never charge to find a relative."
        },
        {
          "q": "What does the Benefactor plan add, then?",
          "a": "Comfort extras: high-definition PDF export with no watermark (to frame or print), an extended photo gallery on profiles, and a family booklet sent once or twice a year. And you help cover hosting."
        },
        {
          "q": "Can I stop at any time?",
          "a": "Yes. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current period. You keep the same full access to the tree: only the plan's comfort extras stop."
        },
        {
          "q": "Is the payment secure?",
          "a": "Yes, it is handled by Stripe. Gate never stores your banking information."
        }
      ]
    }
